message.content:
Ecco una landing page single-file in stile cyberpunk per un negozio di programmazione AI, con modulo contatti e popup di conferma.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Code Emporium • Cyberpunk</title>
    <!-- Font futuristico -->
    <link href="httpshttps" rel="stylesheet" href="https://https" >
    <style>
    /* Reset e stardo compatto */
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
        background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #0c0f1f 0%, #1b1e2b 100%, #0ff00 0%);
        color: #e0f0ff;
        font-family: 'Orba', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 0;
        background-size: cover;
        background-attachment: fixed;
    }

    .glass-card {
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        border: 1px solid #0ff;
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 2.5rem 2.2rem;
        max-width: 680px;
        width: 100%;
        box-shadow: 0 0 40px #0ff88, 0 0 20px #0ff44;
        transition: 0.2s;
        margin: 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .glass-card:hover {
        box-shadow: 0 0 60px #0ff, 0 0 30px #0ff;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff, 0 0 20px #0ff;
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .sub-title {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #b0d0ff;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px dashed #0ff8;
        padding-bottom: 0.8rem;
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .grid {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 1.2rem;
        justify-content: center;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    .card-code {
        background: #0a0f1f;
        border: 1px solid #0ff;
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
        flex: 1 1 180px;
        min-width: 180px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px #0ff22;
        transition: 0.2s;
        color: #d0eaff;
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    .card-code:hover {
        background: #0ff1;
        transform: scale(1.02);
        border-color: #f0f;
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px #f0f;
    }

    .card-code i {
        font-size: 2rem;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .form-wrapper {
        background: #0a0f1f;
        border: 1px solid #0ff;
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
        text-align: left;
    }

    .form-row {
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.3rem;
    }

    label {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        color: #0ff;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    input, textarea {
        background: #0003;
        border: 1px solid #0ff88;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 1rem;
        outline: none;
        transition: 0.2s;
        font-family: inherit;
    }

    input:focus, textarea:focus {
        border-color: #f0f;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #f0f;
    }

    textarea {
        min-height: 120px;
        resize: vertical;
    }

    .btn {
        background: #0ff;
        color: #0a0f1f;
        border: none;
        padding: 0.8rem 2.5rem;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        border-radius: 40px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: 0.2s;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff88;
        width: 100%;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .btn:hover {
        background: #f0f;
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px #f0f;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .footer-text {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: #8f9fbf;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #0ff44;
        padding-top: 1rem;
    }

    .popup-overlay {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: #00000080;
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    z-index: 999;
    animation: fadeIn 0.2s;
}

    .popup-card {
        background: #0a0f1f;
        border: 2px solid #0ff;
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 2.5rem 2.2rem;
        max-width: 350px;
        width: 90%;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 0 60px #0ff;
        animation: popup 0.3s;
    }

    .popup-card h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: #0ff;
    }

    .popup-card p {
        color: #d0eaff;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .close-popup {
        background: #0ff;
        color: #000;
        border: none;
        padding: 0.5rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 40px;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: 0.2s;
    }

    .close-popup:hover {
        background: #f0f;
    }

    .active {
        display: flex;
    }

    .glp_btn {
        background: #0ff;
        border: none;
        padding: 0.8rem 2.5rem;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        border-radius: 40px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: 0.2s;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff88;
        width: 100%;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .glp_btn:hover {
        background: #f0f;
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px #f0f;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .error {
        border-color: #f0f;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .glass-card {
    padding: 1.2rem;
    }
    h1 {
        font-size: 2.4rem;
    }
    .card-code {
        min-width: 100;
    }
    </style>
    /*  */
</style>
<!-- HTML -->
